name: Carlos Garcia
summary:
Carlos Garcia is a 34-year-old, Hispanic/Latino man who identifies as gay and uses he/him/his pronouns. He is a software engineer in the technology industry, graduated from the University of California, Berkeley, and is currently located in Los Angeles. He is originally from San Diego. Carlos is fluent in both English and Spanish. He values honesty, simplicity, and humor.

His interests include coding, photography, and hiking. He categorizes himself as agnostic and politically liberal. He does not currently have children but is interested in having them in the future. He is an active individual who occasionally drinks but does not smoke or use drugs. His preferred partner is a man, between 27 and 40 years old, who also desires to have children and leads an active lifestyle.

Carlos is an Aquarius and is classified as an INTP according to the MBTI personality scale. His ideal date is also a non-smoker and moderate drinker. He is a proud dog owner and meets potential matches in Los Angeles with the intention of cultivating a long-term relationship with someone who values a monogamous relationship.
